                    <md>
                        <mrow>f(2)=\sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{2^n}{n!} \amp = 1+2+\frac{2^2}{2}+\frac{2^3}{6}+\frac{2^4}{24}+\frac{2^5}{120}+\cdots </mrow>
                        <mrow>\amp = \unknown +\cdots </mrow>
                        <mrow>\amp \approx \unknown </mrow>
                    </md>
